3c/div\u003e\",\"seo\":{\"__typename\":\"ComponentSharedSeo\",\"metaTitle\":\"Aadhaar enabled Payment Service (AePS) - Muthoot Fincorp\",\"metaDescription\":\"Muthoot FinCorp's Aadhaar enabled Payment Service (AePS) provides a secure, and hassle-free way to manage your basic banking service. \",\"sharedImage\":null,\"isPreview\":false,\"keywords\":\"AePS\\nMuthoot FinCorp Aadhaar enabled Payment Services\\naadhaar-enabled-payment-service\",\"preventIndexing\":false,\"meta\":[{\"__typename\":\"ComponentSharedMeta\",\"name\":\"Muthoot FinCorp Aadhaar enabled Payment Services.\",\"content\":\"Muthoot FinCorp Ltd makes banking simple, secure, and accessible through its AePS services. With just your Aadhaar number and fingerprint authentication, you can carry out transactions without the need for extra documents or cards. This service not only ensures safe and fraud-resistant banking through biometric verification but also promotes financial inclusion by reaching unbanked and underbanked communities. By bridging the gap between traditional banking and underserved segments, Muthoot FinCorp empowers customers with seamless digital financial services. Visit your nearest branch to experience the convenience of upgraded banking.\"}]}}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"23\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Credit Report\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/icon_credit_report_76f52c923d.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=9bf9128021aa77df2e044a5684310a95ed0ddc668856030aa06ff143d389fd9e\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"credit-report\",\"content\":\"\u003cdiv class=\\\"raw-html-embed\\\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eA Credit Report is a detailed record of an individual's credit history, including their borrowing and repayment activities.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\n\u003cp\u003eCredit Report is maintained by credit reporting agencies, also known as Credit Bureaus, and contains information about the person's credit accounts, loans, credit cards, payment history, and other relevant financial data.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\n\u003cp\u003eCredit Report essentially serves as a snapshot of a person's financial behavior and creditworthiness.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\",\"seo\":{\"__typename\":\"ComponentSharedSeo\",\"metaTitle\":\"Payment and Services\",\"metaDescription\":null,\"sharedImage\":{\"__typename\":\"ComponentSharedShareImage\",\"media\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":null},\"alt\":null},\"isPreview\":false,\"keywords\":null,\"preventIndexing\":false,\"meta\":[{\"__typename\":\"ComponentSharedMeta\",\"name\":null,\"content\":null}]}}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"13\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Foreign Currency Exchange\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Round_7_5aa1b8766f.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=3de40a0aede96adb2c8864e134b113ce43aa3776575fe94802107f5e513632b0\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"foreign-currency-exchange\",\"content\":\"\u003cp\u003eForeign exchange involves buying one currency while simultaneously selling another, requiring both skill and expertise. Muthoot FinCorp offers you the best rates, leveraging our in-depth knowledge of wholesale and retail financial markets to ensure you get the most value.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMuthoot FinCorp equips you with the currency of the place you want to travel. We buy foreign currencies and travelers’ cheques from resident Indians, Non-resident Indians, and foreigners through our wide and extensive network of branches. We hold an Authorized Dealer Category II license from RBI, allowing all our branches nationwide to offer \u0026nbsp;Foreign Exchange services.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"seo\":null}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"16\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Send Money Abroad\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Round_879d268f50.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=d3f77afa3e46ee3251fea4810c4834b106b3062cb2ba1b9f913f17948b228908\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"send-money-abroad\",\"content\":\"\u003cp\u003eWe facilitate currency transfers with ease. Whether you're traveling or sending money abroad, our extensive branch network ensures you receive the currency you need—quickly and securely.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWe serve resident and non-resident Indians, as well as foreign nationals, offering reliable foreign currency exchange and travellers’ cheque services. As an RBI-authorized dealer, all our branches across India are equipped to handle Forex transactions seamlessly.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWith deep market knowledge and expertise, Muthoot FinCorp offers competitive rates, making your foreign exchange experience simple, efficient, and dependable.\u003cbr\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\",\"seo\":null}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"18\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Domestic Money Transfer\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Round_9_7854f36b94.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=cfa875f48475a41ce256500bade721102843e070b4b34e6aabf4fde8498656ae\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"domestic-money-transfer\",\"content\":\"\u003cdiv class=\\\"raw-html-embed\\\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eMuthoot FinCorp’s money transfer services are quick, simple and secure for customers to send money across India. The facility enables our customers to remit cash towards any bank account within India. The service is offered to Muthoot FinCorp Limited customers without any further KYC related delays and cash is sent instantly via IMPS. The customer can remit up to Rs 25,000/- in a month with per transaction limit capped at Rs 5,000/-.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\n\u003cp\u003eThis offering mainly serves the common man in rural India who has no or less access to formal banking channels and helps his/her beneficiary to receive the hard-earned money without delay. The offering is extended during off-banking hours and bank holidays and is available in all 3700+ Muthoot FinCorp branches.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\",\"seo\":{\"__typename\":\"ComponentSharedSeo\",\"metaTitle\":null,\"metaDescription\":null,\"sharedImage\":null,\"isPreview\":false,\"keywords\":null,\"preventIndexing\":false,\"meta\":[]}}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"17\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Inward Remittance\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Round_18_67d8f680db.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=308c8e0480ea29c0a25bd50a125736056e62e903b1220a0575c30b1de8d98a4e\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"inward-remittance\",\"content\":\"\u003cp\u003eAn inward remittance refers to the transfer of money from a foreign bank to the account of an Indian resident. Our Money Transfer Service Scheme (MTSS) offers a quick and convenient way to transfer personal remittances from abroad to beneficiaries in India through International money transfer systems.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe system facilitates a partnership between reputed international money transfer companies and agents in India, who disburse the funds to beneficiaries at the prevailing exchange rate. Only personal remittances for family maintenance or in favor of foreign tourists in India are permissible under this scheme.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"seo\":null}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"14\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Indo-Nepal Remittance\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Round_9_7854f36b94.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=cfa875f48475a41ce256500bade721102843e070b4b34e6aabf4fde8498656ae\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"indo-nepal-remittance\",\"content\":\"\u003cp\u003eMoney transfer is quick and convenient through Muthoot FinCorp. You can send money to Nepal quickly and easily with Muthoot FinCorp's hassle-free services. Collaborating with Prabhu Money Transfer Pvt. Ltd (PMT), we offer seamless transfers from India to Nepal. Easily remit cash to family and friends, accepting payments from both Indian and Nepali citizens in India.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"seo\":null}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"19\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Failed Bill Payments\",\"icon\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntityResponse\",\"data\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFileEntity\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"UploadFile\",\"url\":\"https://mflprodweb.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Round_11_5f4fe9180b.svg?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD\u0026X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5THCCQSFU4EP2MA7%2F20260603%2Fap-south-1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260603T112844Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=900\u0026X-Amz-Signature=936dd83daddaaabab502081a82851fbdf642557627e7dfc9472aaf53fbe12203\u0026X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host\u0026x-id=GetObject\",\"alternativeText\":null}}},\"slug\":\"utility-bill-payments\",\"content\":\"\u003cp\u003eMuthoot FinCorp's Utility bill payment service provides a seamless, secure, and hassle-free way to manage and pay your electricity, water, gas, and other essential bills online. With a simple, user-friendly platform, you can complete your payments in just a few clicks, ensuring timely transactions and avoiding late fees. Supported by multiple payment options and instant confirmation alerts, Muthoot FinCorp makes your bill payments quick and convenient.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"seo\":null}},{\"__typename\":\"ProductEntity\",\"id\":\"15\",\"attributes\":{\"__typename\":\"Product\",\"title\":\"Pan Card Services\",\"ic